<i>This is a work of fiction.</i>

4
00:01:38,980 --> 00:01:42,459
<i>Episode 16</i>

5
00:01:43,060 --> 00:01:44,179
Starting today,

6
00:01:45,259 --> 00:01:47,379
you're just a slave in the Eagle Army.

7
00:01:50,860 --> 00:01:52,379
What do you want me to do?

8
00:01:56,340 --> 00:01:58,659
I want you to disappear from Tang.

9
00:01:59,459 --> 00:02:01,500
I have the final say in deciding whether I'm dead or not.

10
00:02:02,060 --> 00:02:03,140
What you say is useless.

11
00:02:04,940 --> 00:02:06,220
That depends on your capability.

12
00:02:06,899 --> 00:02:08,300
Keeping me by your side...

13
00:02:08,860 --> 00:02:10,340
is like raising a tiger.

14
00:02:10,580 --> 00:02:11,860
It makes no difference.

15
00:02:11,860 --> 00:02:13,019
Make sure you survive first...

16
00:02:13,019 --> 00:02:14,259
before you are worried about that.

17
00:02:15,980 --> 00:02:17,420
The law of survival on the grasslands...

18
00:02:18,339 --> 00:02:19,980
is only the strongest survives.

19
00:02:58,420 --> 00:02:59,700
Behind me...

20
00:03:00,899 --> 00:03:02,540
is Shuozhuo...

21
00:03:03,100 --> 00:03:05,219
that has been looted but the people escaped the battle unscathed.

22
00:03:06,580 --> 00:03:07,899
Behind it...

23
00:03:09,059 --> 00:03:10,700
is endless mountains.

24
00:03:12,260 --> 00:03:13,300
Beyond that...

25
00:03:14,580 --> 00:03:16,619
is my homeland, a million miles away.

26
00:03:18,459 --> 00:03:19,540
Chang'an.

27
00:03:20,459 --> 00:03:22,260
In the end, I couldn't go back there.

28
00:03:30,540 --> 00:03:32,260
In the past, you achieved glory for the motherland.

29
00:03:32,260 --> 00:03:33,660
Now, you're just a slave.

30
00:03:35,580 --> 00:03:36,580
Li Chang Ge.

31
00:03:37,499 --> 00:03:39,420
Even I feel bad for you.

32
00:03:44,059 --> 00:03:45,779
<i>Fuju Inn</i>

33
00:03:45,779 --> 00:03:46,899
After receiving the order,

34
00:03:46,899 --> 00:03:48,219
I hurried here right away.

35
00:03:48,219 --> 00:03:49,219
Please give me your instructions, Commander Hao.

36
00:03:49,860 --> 00:03:51,499
Follow Ashina Tribe at once.

37
00:03:51,779 --> 00:03:53,820
I want to know what happened to Li Chang Ge in the end.

38
00:03:54,660 --> 00:03:55,860
Should I kill her?

39
00:03:55,860 --> 00:03:57,820
If she colludes with Ashina Tribe,

40
00:03:58,899 --> 00:03:59,939
kill her.

41
00:04:00,459 --> 00:04:02,100
What if she doesn't?

42
00:04:02,339 --> 00:04:03,980
Ashina Tribe won't keep her.

43
00:04:04,700 --> 00:04:05,739
Yes.

44
00:04:07,380 --> 00:04:08,420
Send whatever news you have...

45
00:04:08,420 --> 00:04:09,459
through the pigeon.

46
00:04:10,499 --> 00:04:11,499
You may leave.

47
00:04:13,700 --> 00:04:14,899
Yes.

48
00:04:20,580 --> 00:04:21,619
The people dearest to me...

49
00:04:21,739 --> 00:04:23,860
were all slaughtered like pigs and dogs.

50
00:04:24,470 --> 00:04:26,100
The place I was born and raised...

51
00:04:26,300 --> 00:04:27,780
banished me.

52
00:04:27,939 --> 00:04:29,739
I felt like dying every single day.

53
00:04:31,139 --> 00:04:32,910
But I had to do what I had to do.

54
00:04:34,499 --> 00:04:36,030
Once this is over,

55
00:04:36,860 --> 00:04:38,499
it won't be too late to kill me.

56
00:04:38,619 --> 00:04:41,660
<i>Noble and integrate</i>

57
00:04:42,059 --> 00:04:43,259
Li Chang Ge.

58
00:04:43,910 --> 00:04:46,030
I hope you can sacrifice for the people.

59
00:04:50,780 --> 00:04:51,939
Recently,

60
00:04:52,259 --> 00:04:53,579
all the county offices around the kingdom...

61
00:04:53,579 --> 00:04:55,860
are secretly looking for the princess.

62
00:04:56,660 --> 00:04:58,470
However, the portrait that was sent to the capital...

63
00:04:58,579 --> 00:05:00,780
looks nothing like the princess.

64
00:05:01,660 --> 00:05:03,939
Furthermore, the princess lost in the four states in the north.

65
00:05:03,939 --> 00:05:04,939
Until now,

66
00:05:06,139 --> 00:05:08,300
we haven't heard anything yet.

67
00:05:09,100 --> 00:05:10,100
Your Highness.

68
00:05:10,819 --> 00:05:13,540
Princess Yong'an is very blessed.

69
00:05:14,619 --> 00:05:16,619
Didn't Li Chun Feng make a prediction...

70
00:05:16,619 --> 00:05:18,939
that she'll come back safely?

71
00:05:19,100 --> 00:05:20,660
I hope so.

72
00:05:22,739 --> 00:05:23,980
Lately,

73
00:05:25,259 --> 00:05:26,350
I always dreamed of...

74
00:05:26,350 --> 00:05:28,699
Le Yan and Chang Ge when they were younger.

75
00:05:30,499 --> 00:05:31,540
Both of them...

76
00:05:31,980 --> 00:05:33,699
were hanging around in the garden.

77
00:05:34,619 --> 00:05:35,900
I waved at them...

78
00:05:36,579 --> 00:05:37,939
but they couldn't see me.

79
00:05:38,499 --> 00:05:40,220
I called out their names.

80
00:05:40,619 --> 00:05:41,980
But they couldn't hear me either.

81
00:05:42,460 --> 00:05:43,619
Worse,

82
00:05:43,739 --> 00:05:45,259
they kept running away.

83
00:05:49,939 --> 00:05:51,340
Your Highness...

84
00:05:51,460 --> 00:05:52,819
worries too much.

85
00:05:52,819 --> 00:05:53,860
That's why...

86
00:05:53,860 --> 00:05:56,300
Your Highness had weird dreams.

87
00:05:56,660 --> 00:05:59,379
Your Highness, I'll get the imperial kitchen...

88
00:05:59,379 --> 00:06:02,579
to make some soothing soup for Your Highness.

89
00:06:03,220 --> 00:06:04,499
Will those two girls...

90
00:06:06,020 --> 00:06:07,900
be further away from me?

91
00:06:08,300 --> 00:06:09,780
No.

92
00:06:10,619 --> 00:06:13,220
They will always be...

93
00:06:13,220 --> 00:06:14,780
the most daring daughter and official to you.

94
00:06:19,780 --> 00:06:21,780
Perhaps at this moment,

95
00:06:22,420 --> 00:06:24,139
no news is the best news.

96
00:06:24,460 --> 00:06:25,860
That's right.

97
00:06:28,980 --> 00:06:31,100
Your Highness, there is urgent military news.

98
00:06:31,100 --> 00:06:33,100
Ashina Tribe suddenly attacked the north border.

99
00:06:33,540 --> 00:06:35,379
The chief commander, Sima Tu...

100
00:06:35,379 --> 00:06:37,420
and the governor of Shuozhou, Gongsun Heng...

101
00:06:37,819 --> 00:06:39,020
were killed in the battle.

102
00:06:39,020 --> 00:06:40,860
When did it happen?

103
00:06:40,860 --> 00:06:42,499
No one reported it!

104
00:06:42,499 --> 00:06:44,300
Ashina Tribe besieged the city.

105
00:06:44,579 --> 00:06:46,780
The frontier couldn't deliver the message.

106
00:06:47,020 --> 00:06:49,860
Hao Du sent his men to speed things up.

107
00:06:49,860 --> 00:06:51,460
Five horses were sacrificed...

108
00:06:51,460 --> 00:06:53,460
before the news reached Chang'an.

109
00:06:54,460 --> 00:06:56,660
Send our army there now to regain the north region.

110
00:06:56,660 --> 00:06:59,220
Make sure we chase the Ashina Tribe out of the border.

111
00:06:59,660 --> 00:07:00,739
After that,

112
00:07:00,739 --> 00:07:02,179
the troops will camp at the same place...

113
00:07:02,420 --> 00:07:04,540
to comfort the people in the north.

114
00:07:04,540 --> 00:07:05,739
Yes, Your Highness.

115
00:07:10,300 --> 00:07:11,300
Mr. Du.

116
00:07:12,139 --> 00:07:13,139
Mr. Du.

117
00:07:13,499 --> 00:07:16,460
I need to talk to you.

118
00:07:18,420 --> 00:07:21,540
You always know your own mind.

119
00:07:22,179 --> 00:07:23,739
What do you want to discuss with me?

120
00:07:23,739 --> 00:07:26,100
Mr. Du, don't be sarcastic.

121
00:07:26,579 --> 00:07:28,100
You and I are the ministers of the imperial court.

122
00:07:28,100 --> 00:07:30,499
It's good to have someone to discuss with.

123
00:07:30,619 --> 00:07:31,939
Furthermore,

124
00:07:32,100 --> 00:07:34,139
I really need a favor from you.

125
00:07:35,460 --> 00:07:36,900
Just tell me what it is.

126
00:07:37,460 --> 00:07:38,660
As you know,

127
00:07:38,860 --> 00:07:40,420
Princess Yong'an is missing in action.

128
00:07:40,420 --> 00:07:42,780
It's His Highness's biggest concern.

129
00:07:43,139 --> 00:07:44,220
The portrait of Princess Yong'an...

130
00:07:44,220 --> 00:07:45,819
has been sent to all local government offices...

131
00:07:45,980 --> 00:07:47,379
for a secret investigation.

132
00:07:47,379 --> 00:07:48,499
However, Princess Yong'an is nowhere to be found.

133
00:07:48,660 --> 00:07:50,300
But we didn't receive any news...

134
00:07:50,300 --> 00:07:52,059
from the north.

135
00:07:53,300 --> 00:07:54,860
I'm just worried.

136
00:07:56,460 --> 00:07:57,819
What do you want me to do?

137
00:07:57,980 --> 00:07:59,499
People in the north...

138
00:07:59,499 --> 00:08:01,860
have never seen Princess Yong'an before.

139
00:08:02,379 --> 00:08:05,460
Your godson is in the north, right?

140
00:08:05,460 --> 00:08:07,460
Although Wei Shu Yu...

141
00:08:08,340 --> 00:08:10,499
allegedly lost her,

142
00:08:10,900 --> 00:08:12,100
at that time,

143
00:08:12,100 --> 00:08:13,379
your godson, Hao Du...

144
00:08:13,499 --> 00:08:15,619
was with Princess Yong'an.

145
00:08:15,619 --> 00:08:16,980
The more collaborative the effort,

146
00:08:17,699 --> 00:08:18,739
the better.

147
00:08:18,939 --> 00:08:21,220
Furthermore, under your guidance,

148
00:08:21,220 --> 00:08:23,220
- your godson is already... - That's enough.

149
00:08:23,460 --> 00:08:25,059
Talk properly.

150
00:08:25,059 --> 00:08:26,059
Don't flatter me.

151
00:08:27,340 --> 00:08:28,340
Since His Highness...

152
00:08:28,499 --> 00:08:30,699
has entrusted you with this case,

153
00:08:31,179 --> 00:08:32,499
you should work on it.

154
00:08:39,219 --> 00:08:40,300
Yes.

155
00:08:41,510 --> 00:08:42,510
Eat up.

156
00:08:42,900 --> 00:08:43,939
Here.

157
00:08:46,859 --> 00:08:47,859
What's the point of keeping him here?

158
00:08:47,859 --> 00:08:50,059
If you ask me, I'll just kill him.

159
00:08:50,780 --> 00:08:52,300
- Hold on. - Here.

160
00:08:52,699 --> 00:08:53,750
Leave it there.

161
00:08:55,579 --> 00:08:56,750
Give me more.

162
00:08:57,059 --> 00:08:58,059
Here.

163
00:09:04,420 --> 00:09:05,579
Where are you going?

164
00:09:08,300 --> 00:09:09,979
I didn't expect to see you here.

165
00:09:12,979 --> 00:09:14,020
Here.

166
00:09:17,750 --> 00:09:18,939
Actually, the Eagle Army...

167
00:09:19,059 --> 00:09:20,300
isn't too far from Shuozhou.

168
00:09:20,859 --> 00:09:22,390
It's near a river and there are trees.

169
00:09:22,390 --> 00:09:23,630
You'll get used to it.

170
00:09:24,660 --> 00:09:25,699
Eat up.

171
00:09:28,300 --> 00:09:29,390
Let me tell you.

172
00:09:29,390 --> 00:09:30,859
If His Highness didn't care about you,

173
00:09:31,020 --> 00:09:32,339
I wouldn't care about you either.

174
00:09:32,979 --> 00:09:34,260
My goodness.

175
00:09:38,510 --> 00:09:40,819
Your friend is insensible.

176
00:09:41,020 --> 00:09:43,780
I think you're wasting your effort on him.

177
00:09:44,020 --> 00:09:45,510
Look at that body.

178
00:09:45,699 --> 00:09:47,660
I don't think he can survive in the grasslands.

179
00:09:47,900 --> 00:09:49,020
No, he'll survive.

180
00:09:49,219 --> 00:09:50,260
How do you know that?

181
00:09:50,819 --> 00:09:52,750
He is someone who has a strong desire to live.

182
00:09:56,099 --> 00:09:57,140
He won't be defeated...

183
00:09:57,979 --> 00:09:59,020
so easily.

184
00:09:59,510 --> 00:10:00,819
It looks like...

185
00:10:00,819 --> 00:10:02,339
you know him very well.

186
00:10:02,819 --> 00:10:03,900
But I think...

187
00:10:04,059 --> 00:10:06,140
you're just the enemy to him.

188
00:10:07,579 --> 00:10:08,630
It doesn't matter.

189
00:10:11,179 --> 00:10:13,630
You've never treated me so nicely after all these years.

190
00:10:30,699 --> 00:10:31,699
That person...

191
00:10:31,859 --> 00:10:33,099
has been following us for a long time.

192
00:10:34,140 --> 00:10:35,179
I know.

193
00:10:35,660 --> 00:10:36,819
He's here to see Shi Si Lang.

194
00:10:39,020 --> 00:10:40,179
Do something for me.

195
00:10:44,900 --> 00:10:45,939
What are you doing?

196
00:10:46,059 --> 00:10:47,099
Let go!

197
00:10:47,579 --> 00:10:48,660
Listen to me.

198
00:10:48,900 --> 00:10:50,219
You're our slave.

199
00:10:50,219 --> 00:10:51,780
Just do whatever I tell you to do.

200
00:10:52,260 --> 00:10:53,300
What?

201
00:10:53,579 --> 00:10:54,859
Are you refusing to work?

202
00:10:55,390 --> 00:10:56,939
You must have a death wish.

203
00:10:57,859 --> 00:10:58,939
Take him away.

204
00:10:59,099 --> 00:11:00,140
Cut him into pieces and feed him to the dogs!

205
00:11:00,260 --> 00:11:01,300
- Yes, sir. - Yes, sir.

206
00:11:03,339 --> 00:11:04,420
What are you doing?

207
00:11:04,420 --> 00:11:05,500
What are you doing?

208
00:11:05,660 --> 00:11:06,699
Let go of me!

209
00:11:07,459 --> 00:11:08,500
Let go!

210
00:11:08,900 --> 00:11:10,059
Come on!

211
00:11:10,059 --> 00:11:11,140
Let go!

212
00:11:14,179 --> 00:11:15,179
Come on!

213
00:11:44,020 --> 00:11:45,020
Elder Qin.

214
00:11:52,339 --> 00:11:54,059
I feel bad for Yuan Niang.

215
00:11:55,140 --> 00:11:57,020
She has been homeless and travels with us for so long.

216
00:11:57,900 --> 00:11:58,939
Not at all.

217
00:11:59,300 --> 00:12:02,859
She has the best father and mother in the world.

218
00:12:05,140 --> 00:12:06,620
How is Shuozhou doing?

219
00:12:08,140 --> 00:12:09,300
I heard that...

220
00:12:09,459 --> 00:12:10,900
the Ashina Tribe has left.

221
00:12:11,459 --> 00:12:13,740
Someone from the imperial court will come and take over the rest.

222
00:12:15,020 --> 00:12:16,059
Aside from that...

223
00:12:17,699 --> 00:12:18,859
"Aside from that"?

224
00:12:19,020 --> 00:12:20,219
Are you going to tell me...

225
00:12:20,380 --> 00:12:21,900
about Young Master?

226
00:12:23,219 --> 00:12:25,179
He failed in the assassination.

227
00:12:25,179 --> 00:12:26,179
He was killed.

228
00:12:27,420 --> 00:12:29,500
I see. He's...

229
00:12:30,300 --> 00:12:31,459
He's too strong and impulsive.

230
00:12:32,300 --> 00:12:33,819
It's easy to destroy those who are strong and impulsive.

231
00:12:34,579 --> 00:12:35,620
If...

232
00:12:37,740 --> 00:12:39,620
Stop it.

233
00:12:39,979 --> 00:12:41,300
I think Young Master...

234
00:12:41,420 --> 00:12:42,979
is still alive.

235
00:12:43,339 --> 00:12:44,900
He's still alive?

236
00:12:45,219 --> 00:12:47,179
Since Ashina Sun...

237
00:12:47,420 --> 00:12:49,380
made a promise with Governor Gongsun,

238
00:12:49,380 --> 00:12:51,540
he won't kill him for sure.

239
00:12:51,900 --> 00:12:54,780
Perhaps he has brought him to the grasslands.

240
00:12:55,179 --> 00:12:56,500
Let's not wait any longer.

241
00:12:56,660 --> 00:12:58,459
- Let's look for him. - In the grasslands,

242
00:12:58,459 --> 00:13:00,380
they have spies everywhere.

243
00:13:00,540 --> 00:13:03,140
We can't barge in as we like.

244
00:13:05,059 --> 00:13:07,059
Let's take care of Yuan Niang first.

245
00:13:07,540 --> 00:13:09,740
We should use our previous connection...

246
00:13:09,740 --> 00:13:11,979
and see if we can get some information.

247
00:13:11,979 --> 00:13:13,059
Then I'll make a decision.

248
00:13:24,979 --> 00:13:28,260
<i>Someone has been executed by Ashina Sun.</i>

249
00:13:34,300 --> 00:13:35,459
Li Chang Ge.

250
00:13:36,219 --> 00:13:37,979
Perhaps this is the best place for you.

251
00:13:56,339 --> 00:13:57,380
Why are you here?

252
00:13:58,140 --> 00:13:59,459
That's my question for you.

253
00:14:00,300 --> 00:14:02,140
Losing the princess is a serious matter...

254
00:14:02,260 --> 00:14:04,059
yet His Highness didn't blame you.

255
00:14:04,579 --> 00:14:06,219
I'll find Le Yan for sure.

256
00:14:07,260 --> 00:14:08,339
I'll wait and see.

257
00:14:09,740 --> 00:14:10,819
It has been so long.

258
00:14:10,979 --> 00:14:12,099
You didn't return to Chang'an.

259
00:14:13,099 --> 00:14:14,339
Are you looking for Chang Ge?

260
00:14:16,660 --> 00:14:17,780
What happened to her?

261
00:14:18,540 --> 00:14:19,540
She's dead.

262
00:14:22,339 --> 00:14:23,500
How did she die?

263
00:14:25,059 --> 00:14:26,140
Did you kill her?

264
00:14:29,540 --> 00:14:30,540
Tell me!

265
00:14:41,900 --> 00:14:42,939
Wei Shu Yu.

266
00:14:43,620 --> 00:14:45,339
Do you plan to sacrifice yourself and your family...

267
00:14:45,339 --> 00:14:47,339
just to avenge your lover?

268
00:14:47,459 --> 00:14:48,660
After killing you,

269
00:14:49,660 --> 00:14:51,459
I'll kill myself to atone for it.

270
00:14:51,459 --> 00:14:53,300
Do you think that His Highness...

271
00:14:53,420 --> 00:14:55,660
will punish the Wei family just for you?

272
00:14:58,059 --> 00:14:59,260
Then why didn't you do it?

273
00:15:00,579 --> 00:15:02,300
When Li Chang Ge was alive, you couldn't do anything.

274
00:15:02,300 --> 00:15:03,339
Now that she's dead,

275
00:15:03,459 --> 00:15:04,540
you found the courage to take revenge.

276
00:15:06,540 --> 00:15:07,579
I guess,

277
00:15:08,140 --> 00:15:09,939
that's because you know that since Li Chang Ge is dead,

278
00:15:10,059 --> 00:15:12,179
your family's glory won't be affected.

279
00:15:20,179 --> 00:15:21,579
Even if you want revenge,

