569
00:30:54,780 --> 00:30:56,260
You scared her.

570
00:30:56,619 --> 00:30:57,700
One cookie is three cents.

571
00:30:57,700 --> 00:30:58,940
Don't think that it's expensive.

572
00:30:58,940 --> 00:30:59,980
The war is still going on.

573
00:31:00,180 --> 00:31:02,059
