587
00:31:41,700 --> 00:31:43,300
I think...

588
00:31:43,700 --> 00:31:45,940
this is the prettiest pouch.

589
00:31:51,700 --> 00:31:53,859
All right. Hold on.

590
00:31:57,139 --> 00:31:58,700
Here's your cookie.

591
00:32:00,659 --> 00:32:01,980
- Thank you. - All right.

592
00:32:04,859 --> 00:32:05,899
Hey.

593
00:32:18,020 --> 00:32:19,339
I'm sorry.

594
00:32:19,339 --> 00:32:20,379
It's all right.

595
00:32:20,379 --> 00:32:22,419
I've had something dirtier before.

596
00:32:24,980 --> 00:32:26,659
If you don't mind,

597
00:32:27,460 --> 00:32:28,579
I'll give you half.

598
00:32:31,700 --> 00:32:33,099
I'll give you some.

599
00:32:34,419 --> 00:32:36,059
- I didn't mean any harm. - Hey.

600
00:32:36,059 --> 00:32:37,139
Nowadays,

601
00:32:37,339 --> 00:32:38,980
