604
00:32:44,020 --> 00:32:45,700
You must be a fool.

605
00:32:47,300 --> 00:32:48,619
Come and take a look.

606
00:32:50,780 --> 00:32:51,780
My pouch.

607
00:32:52,300 --> 00:32:53,379
My pouch!

608
00:32:54,819 --> 00:32:55,980
Stop right there!

609
00:32:57,659 --> 00:32:58,700
Stop right there!

