00:33:00,099 --> 00:33:01,859
My pouch!

611
00:33:03,940 --> 00:33:05,020
Stop right there!

612
00:33:07,940 --> 00:33:09,099
Stop right there!

613
00:33:20,619 --> 00:33:21,700
Stop right there!

614
00:33:23,740 --> 00:33:24,940
Give me back my pouch.

615
00:33:24,940 --> 00:33:26,139
You can take the money.

616
00:33:44,339 --> 00:33:45,419
Right.

617
00:33:45,419 --> 00:33:46,579
Here. This is for you.

618
00:33:50,300 --> 00:33:51,859
It's so ugly. What's this?

619
00:33:51,859 --> 00:33:53,379
My hands got pricked in order to make that,

620
00:33:53,379 --> 00:33:54,500
and you're even complaining that it's ugly.

621
00:33:54,500 --> 00:33:57,099
- Forget it then. - It is ugly,

622
00:33:57,260 --> 00:33:58,619
but I like it.

623
00:34:02,020 --> 00:34:03,339
Chang Ge.

624
00:34:08,139 --> 00:34:09,419
Where are you?

625
00:34:22,180 --> 00:34:23,260
Have you seen the lady...

626
00:34:23,419 --> 00:34:24,419
on the portrait?

627
00:34:24,589 --> 00:34:25,589
No.

628
00:34:27,019 --> 00:34:28,069
Have you seen this lady?

629
00:34:28,069 --> 00:34:29,069
No.

630
00:34:30,339 --> 00:34:31,419
This lady in the portrait,

631
00:34:31,629 --> 00:34:32,700
have you seen her before?

632
00:34:32,700 --> 00:34:33,700
No.

633
00:34:35,379 --> 00:34:37,109
- Have you seen her before? - No.

634
00:34:37,499 --> 00:34:38,589
You!

635
00:34:38,939 --> 00:34:40,499
- No, I haven't seen her. - Are they...

636
00:34:40,499 --> 00:34:41,819
