After her!

643
00:35:32,660 --> 00:35:33,780
You lost your money.

644
00:35:33,780 --> 00:35:35,220
Why are you following me?

645
00:35:35,819 --> 00:35:36,899
They want to arrest me.

646
00:35:37,069 --> 00:35:38,459
What did you do?

647
00:35:38,660 --> 00:35:39,979
I didn't do anything wrong.

648
00:35:40,180 --> 00:35:41,859
They accused me of pretending to be the princess.

649
00:35:41,979 --> 00:35:43,979
Why did you do that?

650
00:35:44,459 --> 00:35:45,819
Young lady.

651
00:35:45,819 --> 00:35:47,419
Are you a fool?

652
00:35:47,629 --> 00:35:49,740
I'm not pretending to be a princess. I really...

653
00:35:56,660 --> 00:35:57,700
Open the door!

654
00:35:59,019 --> 00:36:00,019
Open the door!

655
00:36:01,419 --> 00:36:02,459
Coming.

656
00:36:02,459 --> 00:36:03,740
Are you going to pay me if you break the door?

657
00:36:05,859 --> 00:36:06,979
It's still daytime.

658
00:36:06,979 --> 00:36:08,300
What's the rush?

659
00:36:08,499 --> 00:36:10,109
Are you here to buy clothes?

660
00:36:11,339 --> 00:36:12,629
We're chasing after a girl.

661
00:36:12,819 --> 00:36:14,379
I saw her walking on this street.

662
00:36:14,379 --> 00:36:15,379
Have you seen her before?

663
00:36:17,660 --> 00:36:18,819
We're looking for her.

664
00:36:24,109 --> 00:36:25,260
Yes, I have.

665
00:36:26,629 --> 00:36:30,260
This lady was pickpocketed on the street earlier.

666
00:36:30,260 --> 00:36:32,019
She went after the perpetrator, heading south.

667
00:36:33,069 --> 00:36:35,589
Sir, what did she do?

668
00:36:35,589 --> 00:36:37,419
Is she a robber?

669
00:36:37,539 --> 00:36:39,539
This area is not safe lately.

670
00:36:47,419 --> 00:36:48,859
- Search the place. - Hey!

671
00:36:48,859 --> 00:36:50,700
Sir!

672
00:37:06,660 --> 00:37:08,589
<i>Great virtue brings happiness</i>

673
00:37:08,589 --> 00:37:09,700
What's the matter?

674
00:37:09,979 --> 00:37:12,180
- I don't know. - What's wrong?

675
00:37:30,740 --> 00:37:32,140
- We didn't find anything. - We didn't find anything.

676
00:37:33,339 --> 00:37:34,339
She's not there either.

677
00:37:35,339 --> 00:37:37,780
Sir, as I said, she's not here.

678
00:37:37,780 --> 00:37:39,979
My textile workshop is operating.

679
00:37:40,109 --> 00:37:42,499
You simply look around the workshop.

680
00:37:42,499 --> 00:37:43,939
It will leave a bad impression.

681
00:37:43,939 --> 00:37:44,979
That's enough.

682
00:37:45,339 --> 00:37:46,499
If you see her again,

683
00:37:46,499 --> 00:37:47,499
inform us right away.

684
00:37:47,899 --> 00:37:48,899
Of course.

685
00:37:49,939 --> 00:37:50,979
Let's go.

686
00:38:07,700 --> 00:38:08,700
You're smart.

687
00:38:08,700 --> 00:38:09,819
At least you hid in the tank.

688
00:38:10,780 --> 00:38:11,859
Thank you for the help.

689
00:38:12,069 --> 00:38:13,859
I thought you wouldn't save me.

690
00:38:14,019 --> 00:38:15,019
That's enough.

691
00:38:15,180 --> 00:38:17,109
You don't seem like a bad person.

692
00:38:17,780 --> 00:38:19,660
They have nothing better to do.

693
00:38:19,819 --> 00:38:21,589
You're just pretending to be a princess.

694
00:38:21,780 --> 00:38:22,780
Do they really have to do that?

695
00:38:22,939 --> 00:38:24,019
Ma'am.

696
00:38:24,019 --> 00:38:25,220
I'm not pretending.

697
00:38:25,459 --> 00:38:26,939
I'm really a princess.

698
00:38:26,939 --> 00:38:28,069
All right.

699
00:38:28,069 --> 00:38:30,180
It doesn't matter if you're a princess or a lord.

700
00:38:30,180 --> 00:38:31,180
I need to get back to work.

701
00:38:31,180 --> 00:38:32,339
You should go.

702
00:38:32,660 --> 00:38:33,740
Ma'am.

703
00:38:33,740 --> 00:38:35,700
If I go out right now,

704
00:38:35,819 --> 00:38:37,140
I'll get caught.

705
00:38:37,260 --> 00:38:38,339
I beg you.

706
00:38:38,339 --> 00:38:39,979
Please let me stay here for one more day.

707
00:38:40,109 --> 00:38:41,459
I beg you.

708
00:38:42,740 --> 00:38:43,939
All right.

709
00:38:44,069 --> 00:38:45,780
Go inside and get changed.

710
00:38:46,379 --> 00:38:48,069
Don't blame me when you get sick.

711
00:38:49,740 --> 00:38:51,109
Thank you, ma'am.

712
00:39:03,019 --> 00:39:04,589
So this is the grassland.

713
00:39:06,589 --> 00:39:08,180
It's so vast.

714
00:39:11,220 --> 00:39:12,339
Madam Su Yi Li.

715
00:39:12,339 --> 00:39:13,419
Do you have more cheese?

716
00:39:13,419 --> 00:39:15,339
- Please keep some for me. - Sure.

717
00:39:15,339 --> 00:39:16,740
Come to my tent later.

718
00:39:16,859 --> 00:39:17,939
You can have as much as you want.

719
00:39:18,939 --> 00:39:21,069
Your Highness, are there any presents for us?

720
00:39:21,419 --> 00:39:23,780
Ye, everyone gets a present.

721
00:39:24,220 --> 00:39:25,260
Ya Luo.

722
00:39:27,140 --> 00:39:29,109
Your Highness, the herbs are ready.

723
00:39:29,109 --> 00:39:30,180
Here they are.

724
00:39:31,859 --> 00:39:32,899
Take a look.

725
00:39:33,859 --> 00:39:34,939
It's not bad.

726
00:39:36,979 --> 00:39:38,539
- Here, Your Highness. - Take a look.

727
00:39:38,740 --> 00:39:39,780
Help yourself.

728
00:39:39,979 --> 00:39:41,700
- There are presents! - I want this.

729
00:39:44,459 --> 00:39:45,459
This is good.

730
00:39:45,939 --> 00:39:47,019
- Look. - Let me see.

731
00:39:48,069 --> 00:39:49,979
Uncle Shi Min, where is my reward?

732
00:39:49,979 --> 00:39:51,109
- Where is my reward? - Where is my reward?

733
00:39:51,109 --> 00:39:52,629
- Stand still. - Where is my reward?

734
00:39:52,629 --> 00:39:53,740
Stand still and close your eyes.

735
00:39:54,109 --> 00:39:55,339
Close your eyes. Close them.

736
00:40:00,459 --> 00:40:02,019
What about me, Uncle Shi Min? Where's mine?

737
00:40:02,019 --> 00:40:03,379
- Give it to me - I only have one pony.

738
00:40:04,939 --> 00:40:07,180
- I'll give it if you can reach it. - Give it to me, Father!

739
00:40:07,780 --> 00:40:08,819
Give it to me.

740
00:40:12,660 --> 00:40:13,700
Father!

741
00:40:18,499 --> 00:40:19,700
Uncle Shi Min!

742
00:40:19,859 --> 00:40:21,780
Father, don't go against your words.

743
00:40:21,780 --> 00:40:22,780
Father!

744
00:40:23,499 --> 00:40:24,589
Uncle Shi Min!

745
00:40:26,740 --> 00:40:28,220
Give it to me, Uncle Shi Min!

746
00:40:28,459 --> 00:40:29,589
You promised me!

747
00:40:36,819 --> 00:40:38,459
- Here, let me help you. - Thank you.

748
00:40:38,939 --> 00:40:39,979
Not bad.

749
00:40:40,300 --> 00:40:41,339
That was fun.

750
00:40:43,109 --> 00:40:44,140
Hey!

751
00:40:46,109 --> 00:40:47,499
You're good in Cuju, right?

752
00:40:48,260 --> 00:40:49,260
This is for you.

753
00:40:50,300 --> 00:40:52,339
Can we have the ball?

754
00:40:58,379 --> 00:40:59,379
Here.

755
00:41:01,419 --> 00:41:02,819
- Stop right there! - Come on!

756
00:41:02,819 --> 00:41:03,819
Wait for me!

757
00:41:05,220 --> 00:41:06,499
Slow down!

758
00:41:06,899 --> 00:41:08,300
- Give it to me. - No.

759
00:41:10,819 --> 00:41:12,140
I'll send the present home for them.

760
00:41:12,300 --> 00:41:13,780
- Hold it properly. - Can you take it to him?

761
00:41:28,629 --> 00:41:30,459
The pay is so low.

762
00:41:31,140 --> 00:41:32,660
Madam Zhang, you should consider yourself lucky.

763
00:41:32,780 --> 00:41:34,220
At least we still have work to do.

764
00:41:34,220 --> 00:41:35,260
We won't be starving to death.

765
00:41:35,260 --> 00:41:36,339
That's not bad.

766
00:41:37,109 --> 00:41:38,140
You're right.

767
00:41:38,260 --> 00:41:39,859
It's getting difficult to use the machine.

768
00:41:39,979 --> 00:41:41,109
Yes.

769
00:41:49,140 --> 00:41:50,220
Madam Chai.

770
00:41:50,220 --> 00:41:51,819
You finally hired someone.

771
00:41:52,780 --> 00:41:53,819
I found her on the street.

772
00:41:53,819 --> 00:41:54,939
She'll leave tomorrow.

773
00:42:01,180 --> 00:42:02,740
Greetings, everyone.

774
00:42:04,379 --> 00:42:05,939
What are you looking at?

775
00:42:05,939 --> 00:42:06,939
Get back to work!

776
00:42:11,899 --> 00:42:13,740
She's so pretty.

777
00:42:14,780 --> 00:42:16,629
What kind of salutation was that?

778
00:42:16,629 --> 00:42:19,109
I don't know. It looks nice though.

779
00:42:19,109 --> 00:42:20,109
Exactly.

780
00:42:20,220 --> 00:42:21,629
Greetings, everyone.

781
00:42:21,629 --> 00:42:22,629
That's not correct.

782
00:42:22,629 --> 00:42:23,740
It's like this.

783
00:42:23,859 --> 00:42:25,859
- No. - That's what she did.

784
00:42:27,589 --> 00:42:29,180
You'll sleep here tonight.

785
00:42:29,700 --> 00:42:30,979
You have to leave tomorrow.

786
00:42:31,220 --> 00:42:32,589
I don't feed people for nothing.

787
00:42:33,140 --> 00:42:34,589
Thank you, ma'am.

788
00:42:34,589 --> 00:42:36,499
I will repay you someday.

789
00:42:36,660 --> 00:42:37,899
Thank you.

790
00:42:47,740 --> 00:42:49,339
What should I do tomorrow?

791
00:42:49,939 --> 00:42:52,260
<i>Yunzhou County Office</i>

792
00:42:58,220 --> 00:42:59,660
What did you say?

793
00:43:01,069 --> 00:43:02,140
I didn't hear it clearly.

794
00:43:02,660 --> 00:43:04,939
Please pardon me.

795
00:43:04,939 --> 00:43:06,069
Princess Yong'an...

796
00:43:06,069 --> 00:43:08,180
We lost her.

797
00:43:09,939 --> 00:43:11,700
It's fine if you can't find her.

798
00:43:11,859 --> 00:43:13,140
What do you mean you lost her?

799
00:43:13,140 --> 00:43:16,859
We saw a lady who looks like her on the street.

800
00:43:16,859 --> 00:43:19,780
But she got away.

801
00:43:19,780 --> 00:43:21,019
A lady who looks like her?

802
00:43:21,300 --> 00:43:22,379
How did she run away?

803
00:43:22,700 --> 00:43:25,140
Mr. Wei, we'll keep looking.

804
00:43:25,260 --> 00:43:28,459
However, Princess Yong'an has feet.

805
00:43:28,589 --> 00:43:30,140
We are unsure...

806
00:43:30,140 --> 00:43:32,260
whether she's still in Yunzhou or not.

807
00:43:32,260 --> 00:43:33,700
How dare you absolve yourself?

808
00:43:33,899 --> 00:43:34,979
Yes.

809
00:43:34,979 --> 00:43:37,260
We'll keep looking.

810
00:43:38,300 --> 00:43:39,539
- I'll look for her tomorrow! - I'll look for her tomorrow!

811
00:43:39,819 --> 00:43:40,859
- Get lost! - Get lost!

812
00:43:40,859 --> 00:43:41,859
Yes, sir!

813
00:43:46,819 --> 00:43:47,899
Yan Er.

814
00:43:48,780 --> 00:43:49,859
Where are you?

